snippet.textDisplay: Matt, what was the battery charge level of the S60? Only asking as the T8’s (Polestar Engineered Model Included) limit power output regardless of drive mode depending on battery percentage and usage. This could be the difference between T6 levels of power output and T8 levels of power output... from the shot when you showed the S60’s dash, the batter icon looked as though it was basically empty (says only 1mi of battery power left which is about 8.5% charge) which would mean the car was hardly contributing any electric power delivery. I think a retest is definitely in order on full charge.
